                        </div>
                        <p class="price-desc">700 积分/月，适合轻度创作者</p>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="pricing-features">
                        <li class="included">✅ 原 IMA 全部功能</li>
                        <li class="included">✅ 700 积分/月</li>
                        <li class="included">✅ Bot Lite（轻量体验）</li>
                        <li class="included">✅ 基础模型</li>
                        <li class="included">✅ 基础 Skill 工具箱</li>
                        <li class="excluded">❌ 云端实例</li>
