                        <li class="included">✅ 18000 积分/月</li>
                        <li class="included">✅ 2核4G 云端实例</li>
                        <li class="included">✅ 完整 Bot 功能</li>
                        <li class="included">✅ 全模型池（Kimi/MiniMax/Claude）</li>
                        <li class="included">✅ 全 Skill 工具箱</li>
                        <li class="included">✅ 浏览器工具箱</li>
                        <li class="included">✅ 基础建站工具箱</li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="pricing-limits">
                        <li>✓ 并发：2</li>
                        <li>✓ 队列：50</li>
                        <li>✓ 单次时长：≤60 分钟</li>
